This granola is delicious and easy to make. The first time I made it I just tossed everything together in a bowl and spread it onto a cookie sheet to bake (it was too early in the morning for reading recipes correctly I guess)and it turned out just fine. I've also made it for gifts by putting it into lid-lock jars.

